{"tid":1236102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"團體旺角警署請願支持嚴懲暴徒　批評民主黨鼓動年輕人","createTime":"2019-06-17T10:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T11:15:58.000Z","uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6a2b005082de5ddbc0d8f9671e66c19fa91c95fe","tid":1236102,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:47:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463441-20190617.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463441-20190617.htm&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZChfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=a18f2cc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463441-20190617.htm&h=07d4a098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463441-20190617.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n民間團體「不平則鳴」在旺角警署外請願，支持警察在6月12日嚴正執法平定「暴動」，維持社會秩序。示威者稱讚警方克盡己任，代表全港市民向警方遞交感謝卡，並要求警方嚴懲發起暴動的人。<br />\n<br />\n「不平則鳴」十數名成員拉起橫額「支持警察、嚴懲暴徒」，並高呼口號「多謝警察」、「表揚警察」、「嚴正執法」與「嚴懲暴徒」等口號。<br />\n<br />\n十多分鐘後，代表行往太子彌敦道的民主黨總部，要求對方回應包庇暴徒的指控，示威者批評民主黨「無所不用其極」鼓動年輕人上街，將暴動稱為和平示威。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------<br />\n唔敢去警察總部 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa491a766d4963486ccaaceb069ed55328bd39af","tid":1236102,"uid":211461,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:58:51.000Z","msg":"得果十幾隻 大陸真乾塘了<br />\n陳淨心又無工開 李思焉又無工開<br />\n得一個傅振中有工開<br />\n依家慘到要請啲無人識既老臨"},{"pid":"f4cf49efc56cedea5941e148aaac4316a0b002e2","tid":1236102,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:15:58.000Z","msg":"佢地只係 $2 搭車都唔願過海咁柒懶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}